            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">正力新能(03677)今日登場，全程守在招股價8.27元之上，最低也見8.33元；收報8.39元，高於招股價1.45%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以1手300股計，認購1手賬面微賺36元。</p>\n</div>",
